OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773249077
OL,3,CLionesses Alex Greenwood to receive
OL,4,CMBE at Windsor Castle
OL,6,FThe ceremony marks the latest
OL,7,Fmilestone in an illustrious career for
OL,8,Fthe Bootle-born defender, who has
OL,9,Fbecome one of the most respected and
OL,10,Fconsistent figures in the women's game.
OL,12,FGreenwood's recognition comes off the
OL,13,Fback of a historic period for the
OL,14,FLionesses.
OL,16,FShe has earned 107 caps for her
OL,17,Fcountry, a journey that saw her reach
OL,18,Fthe century mark during England's
OL,19,Ftriumphant Euro 2025 campaign in
OL,20,FSwitzerland.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
